_sText:
The map consists of two bases with many rooms inside, two floodable underground tunnels with 4 rooms, 4 towers, cannons, ah anyways, look at the screenshots!

More are here.. http://www.zombiemod.com/forums/showthread.php?t=1142

The two buttons require that two people work together to reach them, once pressed the underground tunnels will flood. There are tons of places in this map to barricade yourself in and they have all been specifically designed and thought out to work well in game.

If you find any bugs, or have any suggestions, please tell me!
